data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!! Appraisal and inspections have been done! You're gonna LOVE this home for sale in a quiet gated community tucked away just off E. Kings Hwy and minutes from LSUS, WK Pierremont, and all the conveniences you need! Great curb appeal with low maintenance landscaping and a big front porch. Just inside the open foyer behind elegant French doors is a spacious bonus room that works great as a study or formal dining room. The living room is drenched in natural light and features durable hard surface flooring, built in storage and display space, and a gas log fireplace that adds instant ambiance with the flip of a switch. The kitchen is a dream with gleaming granite counter tops and shiny stainless appliances including a smooth top range and built-in microwave. The remote master has a big walk-in closet and a pretty private bath with a jetted tub and stall shower with decorative tile. The backyard is fully fenced with a roomy patio perfect for grilling!
